subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Florida’s Mike Rosario, a former high-scoring Rutgers player, once butted heads with Coach Billy Donovan. But now Rosario has become a leader under Donovan’s discipline.
